								<locus from="114r" to="149r"/>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<title xml:lang="en">Numbers</title>
								<locus from="149r" to="190r"/>
								<note>
									<p>Missing chapters: 28:29 to the end.</p>
								</note>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<title xml:lang="en">Deuteronomy</title>
								<locus from="190r" to="214r"/>
								<note>
									<p>Missing chapters: 1:1-11:17 and 32:8-to the end.</p>
								</note>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="214r" to="289v"/>
								<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Hafṭarot</title>
								<note>
									<p>Imperfect at the beginning.</p>
								</note>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="289v" to="362r"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">Psalms</title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="362v" to="378v"/>
								<title xml:lang="en">A calendar</title>
								<note>
									<p>A calendar of the cycles with rules for fixing the Jewish festivals, written in Persian (Hebrew characters); defective.</p>
									<p>Folios 362v-363r and 376-378 are unconnected to the bulk of this calendar.</p>
								</note>
								<incipit xml:lang="he">אחל לכתוב מחזור גדול דולאבי מאמר הר' ר' יאשיהו ביר' מבורך אלעאקולי ירחמהו אל זק"ל<locus n="363v"/>
								</incipit>
							</msItem>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Paper codex of the 15th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="chart">
								<support>Paper codex.</support>
								<extent>378 folios<dimensions unit="mm" type="leaf">
										<height>175</height>
										<width>125</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>100</height>
										<width>80</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>378 folios (+ 2 unfoliated modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and 2 older and 2 modern unfoliated paper flyleaves at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Indeterminable. Defective at the beginning and after folios 6, 189, 213, 163 etc.</p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="18 20" writtenLines="18 20">
									<p>Uniform layout. </p>
									<p>Number of columns on each page varies from 18 to 20.</p>
									<p>Incomplete at the beginning. Some folios were added later (folios 7-27, 34, 59, 66). </p>
									<p>Ruling is visible. </p>
									<p>Parallel Hebrew foliation. Catchword on every verso. </p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
