							<summary>Oriental (Persian) semi-cursive script, punctuated. <name type="person" role="scribe">Shemu᾿el ben Aharon ben Yosef</name>: inscribed with his name in the colophon, <date calendar="Seleucid">1794</date> [<date calendar="Gregorian">1483</date>] (361r-361v). </summary>
							<handNote script="Hebrew" scope="major"/>
						</handDesc>
						<additions>
							<p>Colophon without names, <date calendar="Seleucid">22 Elul 1794</date> [<date calendar="Gregorian">1483</date>] (folio 286r). </p>
